"65:9:3" : {s: 65, a: 9, w: 3, r: "امر", t: "أَمْرِهَا", l: "أَمْر", lc: 166, tl: "amrihā", lb: "আদেশ, ব্যাপার",e: "(of) its affair", b: "তার কর্মের", i: "urusannya/perbuatannya", f: 2, rm: "command/order/enjoin, authority/power/dominion, counselled/advised/consulted, hold/appoint command, preside as a commander/governor/prince/king, experienced, become many/abundant."},
