"65:12:1" : {s: 65, a: 12, w: 1, r: "اله", t: "ٱللَّهُ", l: "ٱللَّه", lc: 2811, tl: "al-lahu", lb: "আল্লাহ",e: "Allah", b: "আল্লাহ", i: "Allah", f: 733, rm: "to serve, worship or adore; to protect, grant refuge, preserve save, rescue, liberate; object of worship ie God; (ا-ل-ل-ه) God, the one true God applied as a proper name denoting the true god, comprising all the excellent divine names; a unity comprising all the essences of existing things."},
